title: HUGE & QUIET 1 OR 2 BDRM - PLENTY OF CLOSETS
posting_body: ['CLICK HERE FOR A 360 TOUR:', '<URL>', 'DIMENSIONS', 'LIVING ROOM OR 2ND BEDROOM (WITH CLOSET)', '13\'8" X 12\'3"', 'MASTER BEDROOM 13\'9" 12\'11"', 'FOYER 11\'10" x 7\'6"', 'This is an absolutely beautiful and spacious flat that can be used as a one or two bedroom!', 'It is in the rear of the building, so very quiet and private, with indirect light but the unit looks onto tropical palms and vines.', 'The master bedroom has its own dressing room and access to the bathroom.', 'There are newer appliances, plenty of storage, built-in mirrors, and pocket doors, with a nice foyer in a rent-controlled building with elevator.', 'Kitchen:', '* Updated cabinets and quartz countertops', '* Newer stainless steel appliances including:', '* Dishwasher', '* Gas Stove/Oven', '* Built-in Microwave', '* Stainless Refrigerator', '* Garbage Disposal', 'The location is safe and fantastic, especially as San Francisco opens up for business again, Walking distance to Union Square, the Hotel and Theatre Districts, and FIDI (the Financial District) and a healthy walk to Chinatown and North Beach!', 'This is classic San Francisco in the Nob Hill district with endless restaurants, coffee shops, corner stores, transportation and nightlife!', "5 1/2 blocks to Trader Joe's.", 'We pay for steam heat.', 'Laundry in building.', 'Cats ok!', 'Sorry, no dogs.', 'Street Parking only.']
